{"tid":697794,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[HKGOS] 香港人既 open source","createTime":"2018-06-11T07:47:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-14T11:37:24.000Z","uid":116953,"like":31,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"45489fbb47b8edf98da1c0ae029ecccfe9eab600","tid":697794,"uid":116953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T07:47:11.000Z","msg":"是咁的，經過上次比人負皮負到而家都仲負皮緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地仲未放棄既，首先再介紹返<br />\n我地係新組織既香港 open source team<br />\n目標(好似)係係香港建立可以持續發展既社區<br />\n推動開源項目以及促進本港術技交流<br />\n<a href=\"https://github.com/hkgos/about-us\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fhkgos%2Fabout-us&d=kPKbtd5N3Rv9bYbNO5%2FJ58n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=0a0d0795\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/hkgos/about-us</a><br />\n<br />\n講返正題<br />\n我地開始左收集 open source repository 一段時間<br />\n而家已經有超過 30個 repository 係我地張 list 度<br />\n大家有興趣可以睇睇各位巴打既大作<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>awesome-hk-open-source</ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://github.com/hkgos/awesome-hk-open-source\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fhkgos%2Fawesome-hk-open-source&d=kPKbtd5N3Rv9bYbNO5%2FJ58n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=855a29d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/hkgos/awesome-hk-open-source</a><br />\n<br />\n如果發現 D repository 有問題可以係 issues 提出<br />\n<br />\n第二樣就係想擴展一下收集既範圍<br />\n再新增一張香港公司 open source 既 list<br />\n暫時未搵到太多，希望知道既巴打可以提供<br />\n<br />\nGogovan<br />\n<a href=\"https://github.com/gogovan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fgogovan&d=kPKbtd5N3Rv9bYbNO5%2FJ58n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=5eedddbc\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/gogovan</a><br />\n<br />\nLalamove<br />\n<a href=\"https://github.com/lalamove\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Flalamove&d=kPKbtd5N3Rv9bYbNO5%2FJ58n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=3b2da3aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/lalamove</a><br />\n<br />\nQuantr<br />\n<a href=\"https://gitlab.com/quantr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgitlab.com%2Fquantr&d=kPKbtd5N3Rv9bYbNO5%2FJ58n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=1bfe39d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://gitlab.com/quantr</a>"},{"pid":"f4503d85c1b62c6a9399da3f782142fce576d7d4","tid":697794,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T10:23:46.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：無時間做自己project<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e99c6c7eca7d0dfd56375ce69674238b7c50a34a","tid":697794,"uid":96743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T10:49:14.000Z","msg":"Wfc"},{"pid":"bc532c395b2642021834d2c45525749c93005a5a","tid":697794,"uid":1402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e99c6c7eca7d0dfd56375ce69674238b7c50a34a","tid":697794,"uid":96743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T10:49:14.000Z","msg":"Wfc"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T11:44:19.000Z","msg":"唔care又入黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6ecdf45d110f6a21e0d146da7a6d60eacaeaa2d","tid":697794,"uid":125976,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T12:09:28.000Z","msg":"樓主真係好有心，好記得小弟以前讀 U 都滿心熱血想改變香港 IT，希望可以喺香港推動到矽谷文化。<br />\n<br />\n但做咗幾年嘢，法國香港推 IT 真係晒鳩氣，留返啲時間炒樓炒股票好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d05c69589a3ddc2fc52566bd65db2d563af3ce3a","tid":697794,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T17:03:06.000Z","msg":"btw, 個聯登無放入去？"},{"pid":"87077495e455a2c33992417d12a327ed1597a82a","tid":697794,"uid":52977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T18:15:26.000Z","msg":"IT狗路過留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62670bf2f47deb11bcb96f8d13685fe8fe64c912","tid":697794,"uid":39552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T18:22:12.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"b16d8915153c3918025a60578bca7de27e938869","tid":697794,"uid":116953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d05c69589a3ddc2fc52566bd65db2d563af3ce3a","tid":697794,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T17:03:06.000Z","msg":"btw, 個聯登無放入去？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T02:58:20.000Z","msg":"係另一個 repo 度<br />\n<a href=\"https://github.com/hkgos/hkgos-project-list\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fhkgos%2Fhkgos-project-list&d=kPKbtd5N3Rv9bYbNO5%2FJ58n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=70334026\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/hkgos/hkgos-project-list</a><br />\n<br />\n巴打們有好既 idea 都可以提出<br />\n全部意見都會納入考慮之列"},{"pid":"c1c61f42191d448f3f6502c1dda669b534647bfb","tid":697794,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T03:18:48.000Z","msg":"竟然有我個手掣 project <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0902abcdfdf7c75457dc878a0b177022d8bafc1b","tid":697794,"uid":44639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T05:39:00.000Z","msg":"留名學野"},{"pid":"07d93381db5967ace9ffcc03bcec71a1bff7f6d1","tid":697794,"uid":9838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T11:10:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed25d1ca2c33b35ab4e36a27d4fca195c669d374","tid":697794,"uid":10258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T13:11:59.000Z","msg":"我個高登 cache 都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我仲有一堆 scala 既 lib publish 左<br />\n最多人用/星 應該係 aws 個 scala wrapper 同埋 etcd4s<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class